  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COVID-19 Response: Recovery Tracker and RMG Stimulus Package</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">THIS RESEARCH IS PART OF A BROADER RESEARCH FOR RECOVERY TRACKER: 
This research aims to examine the response and recovery packages in a Central American country to better understand the effectiveness of the packages to build back with justice and to contribute to fight against poverty and inequalities.   

FOR RMG STIMULUS PACKAGES AND ADVOCACY: 
This research specifically aims to assess the status of the C-19 stimulus package declared by BD government reach to the garment factory workers who are mostly women, to addressing the pandemic repercussions in their lives and livelihoods and to better understanding the effectiveness of bailouts in RMG sector for workers.</narrative>
  </description>
